No. 788,

Mise.

Standard Fruit & Steamship Co. v. Lynne, Chief Judge, U. S. District Court, et al. Eberhard P. Deutsch, Robert M. Moore, and René H. Himel, Jr., on the motion. Solicitor General Griswold for the United States, and Hugh B. Cox and James H. McGlothlin for United Fruit Co. in opposition.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus denied.
